				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$${10}^{14}/sec$$\end{document} in the region of the solar radiation. It was further demonstrated that this enhancement was due to the contribution of the vanadium d orbitals.

